A

the

I

as

in

position

see

that

a

able
distance

large
number,

all

"'
The
rebels
commenced
an
indiscriminate
slaughter.
Many
colored

soldiers
sprang
into
the
river
and
tried
to
escape
by
swimming,
but
these

were
invariably
shot
dead.

out

When
